Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in cases where 'Completed + In Call' also occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before transitioning to any 'Accepted + In Progress' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Median duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' without transitioning to another activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' leading to a 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities across all cases in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases that follow the variant ending in 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Duration variance of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to the next activity in the most frequent process variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total time from the first 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to the last 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in a case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Average time between consecutive 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in a single case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Time difference between the first 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the first 'Completed + In Call' in a case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases with 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before transitioning to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases without 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the shortest case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the longest case
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS
